data.description: REDUCED PRICE AND $8K SELLER PAID CLOSING COSTS! Get ready to fall in love with your new home sweet home! This stunning property is waiting for you to make it yours! This smart home equipped with smart lock, thermostat and more, is outfitted with a primary bedroom on the main floor, spacious open concept living with gas fireplace, both formal & casual dining areas and even equipped with a screened in porch and back deck - this home is ready for your summer parties! The wrought-iron stair case leads to three more sizable bedrooms, a large recreation room, Jack and Jill bathroom and another full bath. This beautifully designed home has an expansive primary suite, laundry room, rocking chair porch and lots of storage options - just to name a few! Say hello to eco-friendly living with solar panels! Not only will you reduce your carbon footprint, but you'll also enjoy the benefits of a more sustainable and cost-efficient home. With this property, style and sustainability abound!
